    "• Domain Adaptation StrategiesAddressing the challenge of domain shift in remote sensing images is critical.",
    "Our future investigation will delve into assessing the network's capacity to extract features that remain invariant despite domain shifts.",
    "This goal aims to ensure that the learned feature distribution aligns with diverse domains, thus giving the model the adaptability to varying data distributions.",
    "The investigation will specifically explore the potential integration of subspace alignment and instance weighting techniques for effective domain adaptation [49].",
    "Subspace alignment methods aim to align the subspaces of source and target domains, facilitating the extraction of domain-invariant features."
